1
00:00:00,920 --> 00:00:02,379
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

2
00:00:06,129 --> 00:00:07,529
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

3
00:00:08,839 --> 00:00:10,339
<Default><b>No I'm fine!</b></Default>

4
00:00:10,429 --> 00:00:12,179
<Default><b>It's just that, I'm a...</b></Default>

5
00:00:12,259 --> 00:00:14,599
<Default><b>Bit tipsy?
I bet you are!</b></Default>

6
00:00:14,890 --> 00:00:18,730
<Default><b>Sorry, Master Naofumi</b></Default>

7
00:00:18,850 --> 00:00:20,010
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

8
00:00:21,859 --> 00:00:25,359
<Default><b>[GAELION]
Me too. Good night.</b></Default>

9
00:00:26,239 --> 00:00:27,609
<Default><b>My goodness!</b></Default>

10
00:00:27,739 --> 00:00:31,370
<Default><b>Well, these sakes are called
Tanuki and Dragon Killer.</b></Default>

11
00:00:31,620 --> 00:00:33,426
<Default><b>I guess they were
a little too strong</b></Default>

12
00:00:33,450 --> 00:00:35,450
<Default><b>for Raphtalia
and Gaelion, huh?</b></Default>

13
00:00:35,579 --> 00:00:38,039
<Default><b>You know</b></Default>

14
00:00:38,119 --> 00:00:40,759
<Default><b>why you'd wanna keep a place
like this a secret.</b></Default>

15
00:00:41,289 --> 00:00:43,380
<Default><b>I know, isn't
it wonderful?</b></Default>

16
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:45,686
<Default><b>Yeah, it's nice
and secluded.</b></Default>

17
00:00:45,710 --> 00:00:47,146
<Default><b>Atla, can't bother us</b></Default>

18
00:00:47,170 --> 00:00:49,396
<Default><b>and I can learn the
Way of the Dragon Vein here.</b></Default>

19
00:00:49,420 --> 00:00:52,220
<Default><b>Since Gaelion's proven himself
to be a great teacher</b></Default>

20
00:00:52,259 --> 00:00:54,616
<Default><b>I'm sure you'll have it
mastered in no time.</b></Default>

21
00:00:54,640 --> 00:00:56,640
<Default><b>Oh, is he now? Says who?</b></Default>

22
00:00:58,350 --> 00:00:59,990
<Default><b>[underwater explosion]</b></Default>

23
00:01:00,140 --> 00:01:02,165
<Default><b>[GAELION] Stop
firing off your magic power!</b></Default>

24
00:01:02,189 --> 00:01:04,900
<Default><b>Instead of unleashing
all your power like magic</b></Default>

25
00:01:04,980 --> 00:01:07,045
<Default><b>envision yourself
as an empty vessel</b></Default>

26
00:01:07,069 --> 00:01:08,926
<Default><b>one being
filled with power!</b></Default>

27
00:01:08,950 --> 00:01:11,630
<Default><b>[sighs] I don't know
what to make of any of that!</b></Default>

28
00:01:12,069 --> 00:01:13,346
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
You mentioned Raphtalia</b></Default>

29
00:01:13,370 --> 00:01:14,596
<Default><b>already had a blessing</b></Default>

30
00:01:14,620 --> 00:01:17,180
<Default><b>which makes it tricky
for her to learn it too.</b></Default>

31
00:01:17,700 --> 00:01:19,709
<Default><b>[SADEENA] By the way</b></Default>

32
00:01:19,790 --> 00:01:21,710
<Default><b>that Gaelion
is able to talk!</b></Default>

33
00:01:22,459 --> 00:01:24,129
<Default><b>[snoring]</b></Default>

34
00:01:25,209 --> 00:01:28,129
<Default><b>[SADEENA] So, what's the deal
with you two?</b></Default>

35
00:01:28,340 --> 00:01:29,420
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

36
00:01:31,549 --> 00:01:34,719
<Default><b>I mean you and Raphtalia.
What exactly is she to you?</b></Default>

37
00:01:36,349 --> 00:01:37,930
<Default><b>[waves crashing]</b></Default>

38
00:01:39,519 --> 00:01:42,599
<Default><b>It's funny really</b></Default>

39
00:01:43,060 --> 00:01:45,439
<Default><b>[chuckles]
I'm in her debt.</b></Default>

40
00:01:45,900 --> 00:01:48,500
<Default><b>Raphtalia and her parents
gave my life meaning.</b></Default>

41
00:01:48,739 --> 00:01:51,459
<Default><b>If it weren't for them.
I don't know where I'd be.</b></Default>

42
00:01:51,989 --> 00:01:53,669
<Default><b>Gave your life meaning?</b></Default>

43
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:57,620
<Default><b>That's right. So if you intend
on marrying her someday</b></Default>

44
00:01:57,700 --> 00:02:00,220
<Default><b>you'd better be
especially careful.[Sighs]</b></Default>

45
00:02:00,450 --> 00:02:02,409
<Default><b>- Huh?
- That's not it.</b></Default>

46
00:02:02,500 --> 00:02:04,226
<Default><b>I've only ever thought
of Raphtalia</b></Default>

47
00:02:04,250 --> 00:02:05,816
<Default><b>as a daughter of mine.</b></Default>

48
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:08,360
<Default><b>Are you being honest
with yourself right now?</b></Default>

49
00:02:11,719 --> 00:02:13,509
<Default><b>Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

50
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,120
<Default><b>Oh, you're awake!</b></Default>

51
00:02:15,389 --> 00:02:18,180
<Default><b>C'mon, you'll get a cold
if you sleep out here.</b></Default>

52
00:02:18,349 --> 00:02:19,906
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
Let's head back now.</b></Default>

53
00:02:19,930 --> 00:02:21,325
<Default><b>You hear that, Gaelion?</b></Default>

54
00:02:21,349 --> 00:02:22,865
<Default><b>It's time to wake up!</b></Default>

55
00:02:22,889 --> 00:02:25,520
<Default><b>[GAELION]
Huh? Did I fall asleep?</b></Default>

56
00:02:25,810 --> 00:02:27,876
<Default><b>[SADEENA] [giggles]
I'll tell you when we get back</b></Default>

57
00:02:27,900 --> 00:02:29,165
<Default><b>to the village, okay?</b></Default>

58
00:02:29,189 --> 00:02:30,256
<Default><b>[GAELION] Fine.</b></Default>

59
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:33,449
<Default><b>[SADEENA] [giggles] We should
drink like this more often!</b></Default>

60
00:04:06,289 --> 00:04:09,330
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

61
00:04:17,879 --> 00:04:19,220
<Default><b>Ahh!</b></Default>

62
00:04:19,300 --> 00:04:21,340
<Default><b>Looks like you've been
busy here.</b></Default>

63
00:04:24,889 --> 00:04:26,600
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

64
00:04:29,350 --> 00:04:31,745
<Default><b>I've thought about it
and I think it might be best</b></Default>

65
00:04:31,769 --> 00:04:34,439
<Default><b>to put Gaelion's blessing
on all the villagers.</b></Default>

66
00:04:34,730 --> 00:04:36,625
<Default><b>I agree, the more people
who can use</b></Default>

67
00:04:36,649 --> 00:04:38,449
<Default><b>the Way of the
Dragon Vein</b></Default>

68
00:04:38,569 --> 00:04:40,069
<Default><b>[soft roaring]</b></Default>

69
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:42,870
<Default><b>[ELHART]
Hey, kid! How are ya?</b></Default>

70
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:45,319
<Default><b>- Mister Elhart!
- [ELHART] Whoa!</b></Default>

71
00:04:46,660 --> 00:04:48,476
<Default><b>How you been holdin' up
here, missy?</b></Default>

72
00:04:48,500 --> 00:04:50,476
<Default><b>- [RAPHTALIA] Good!
- Well, well.</b></Default>

73
00:04:50,500 --> 00:04:52,105
<Default><b>To what do we
owe the pleasure?</b></Default>

74
00:04:52,129 --> 00:04:54,565
<Default><b>Thought you'd want to see
what I finished for ya.</b></Default>

75
00:04:54,589 --> 00:04:56,670
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

76
00:04:58,470 --> 00:05:00,235
<Default><b>[ELHART]
It sure was a lot of work</b></Default>

77
00:05:00,259 --> 00:05:02,276
<Default><b>but I think
it turned out nicely.</b></Default>

78
00:05:02,300 --> 00:05:03,365
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

79
00:05:03,389 --> 00:05:05,989
<Default><b>Sorry for making you
come all the way out here.</b></Default>

80
00:05:08,810 --> 00:05:10,980
<Default><b>Oh, dear, is that?</b></Default>

81
00:05:17,899 --> 00:05:19,255
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] It doesn't seem
all that different</b></Default>

82
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:21,586
<Default><b>from what you're wearing now
if you ask me.</b></Default>

83
00:05:21,610 --> 00:05:24,250
<Default><b>I did what I could.
Sorry it's not my best work.</b></Default>

84
00:05:24,319 --> 00:05:27,096
<Default><b>It's great! And it's not like
I could've done better.</b></Default>

85
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:28,596
<Default><b>[DEMI-HUMAN GIRL 12-A]
Hey, what's going on?</b></Default>

86
00:05:28,620 --> 00:05:30,620
<Default><b>Are those clothes
for Raphtalia?</b></Default>

87
00:05:30,660 --> 00:05:31,935
<Default><b>Try 'em on we wanna see!</b></Default>

88
00:05:31,959 --> 00:05:33,105
<Default><b>You heard the crowd!</b></Default>

89
00:05:33,129 --> 00:05:35,105
<Default><b>You gotta give the people
what they want, right?</b></Default>

90
00:05:35,129 --> 00:05:36,605
<Default><b>So why not
try go try it on.</b></Default>

91
00:05:36,629 --> 00:05:40,050
<Default><b>Master Naofumi</b></Default>

92
00:05:43,259 --> 00:05:45,300
<Default><b>- [door opening]
Huh?</b></Default>

93
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,680
<Default><b>Hey.</b></Default>

94
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:54,399
<Default><b>Wow.
You look beautiful, Raphtalia!</b></Default>

95
00:05:54,980 --> 00:05:56,660
<Default><b>Do you really think so?</b></Default>

96
00:05:57,019 --> 00:06:00,110
<Default><b>[gasps] Oh, wow!
You look incredible Raphtalia!</b></Default>

97
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:02,216
<Default><b>[KEEL] Those clothes
are awesome on you!</b></Default>

98
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:04,005
<Default><b>Well, seems
everyone likes it.</b></Default>

99
00:06:04,029 --> 00:06:05,589
<Default><b>That settles it then</b></Default>

100
00:06:05,660 --> 00:06:07,596
<Default><b>From now on you're wearing
the miko outfit.</b></Default>

101
00:06:07,620 --> 00:06:10,910
<Default><b>- Hey! I wanna wear one too!
- Okay.</b></Default>

102
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,305
<Default><b>[DEMI-HUMAN GIRL 12-A]
I don't think I've ever seen</b></Default>

103
00:06:12,329 --> 00:06:13,435
<Default><b>clothes like that!</b></Default>

104
00:06:13,459 --> 00:06:14,935
<Default><b>I can't say I understand</b></Default>

105
00:06:14,959 --> 00:06:16,726
<Default><b>what's so special
about this though.</b></Default>

106
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:18,105
<Default><b>[DEMI-HUMAN BOY 12-A]
I'm so jealous.</b></Default>

107
00:06:18,129 --> 00:06:20,759
<Default><b>How come Raphtalia
gets all the attention?</b></Default>

108
00:06:21,420 --> 00:06:23,776
<Default><b>Ya know, since you're
already here, Elhart</b></Default>

109
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,196
<Default><b>you oughta
go visit Tolly.</b></Default>

110
00:06:25,220 --> 00:06:28,680
<Default><b>Yeah! Since you mentioned it
I'm gonna do just that.</b></Default>

111
00:06:28,850 --> 00:06:30,826
<Default><b>You can teach him
some things while you're at it.</b></Default>

112
00:06:30,850 --> 00:06:32,915
<Default><b>And feel free to stay
the night if you'd like to.</b></Default>

113
00:06:32,939 --> 00:06:35,099
<Default><b>[ELHART]
I'll think about it. Later!</b></Default>

114
00:06:36,649 --> 00:06:38,529
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Elhart helped Tolly</b></Default>

115
00:06:38,569 --> 00:06:41,480
<Default><b>and Raphtalia got comfortable
in her new miko outfit.</b></Default>

116
00:06:46,069 --> 00:06:48,490
<Default><b>As for me</b></Default>

117
00:06:48,579 --> 00:06:51,016
<Default><b>with her paperwork
for the rest of the day.</b></Default>

118
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:53,200
<Default><b>Things are tough
without Melty here.</b></Default>

119
00:06:55,250 --> 00:06:58,089
<Default><b>I don't know where Motoyasu is
or what he's doing</b></Default>

120
00:06:59,540 --> 00:07:02,379
<Default><b>but at least Ren and Itsuki
are still accounted for.</b></Default>

121
00:07:04,550 --> 00:07:06,150
<Default><b>We've got two months.</b></Default>

122
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:07,985
<Default><b>Two months to make sure
we're ready</b></Default>

123
00:07:08,009 --> 00:07:10,369
<Default><b>for our upcoming battle
with the Phoenix.</b></Default>

124
00:07:14,519 --> 00:07:17,360
<Default><b>We're back, Naofumi!
Hope you're hungry!</b></Default>

125
00:07:17,439 --> 00:07:18,875
<Default><b>Hey, welcome back!</b></Default>

126
00:07:18,899 --> 00:07:20,619
<Default><b>I pulled in a big catch!</b></Default>

127
00:07:20,649 --> 00:07:22,665
<Default><b>So whip up something special
for dinner!</b></Default>

128
00:07:22,689 --> 00:07:23,755
<Default><b>Sure thing.</b></Default>

129
00:07:23,779 --> 00:07:25,505
<Default><b>We can try frying them
with salt!</b></Default>

130
00:07:25,529 --> 00:07:27,779
<Default><b>You're back, Sadeena</b></Default>

131
00:07:27,860 --> 00:07:30,140
<Default><b>Dinner's going to be splendi...
[gasps]</b></Default>

132
00:07:30,990 --> 00:07:32,055
<Default><b>Are you okay Sadee...</b></Default>

133
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:34,136
<Default><b>Raphtalia, you have to take
these clothes off, right now.</b></Default>

134
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:36,209
<Default><b>Hey, what are you doing</b></Default>

135
00:07:36,290 --> 00:07:37,976
<Default><b>I could ask you
the same thing!</b></Default>

136
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:40,250
<Default><b>I said to be
"especially careful</b></Default>"

137
00:07:40,540 --> 00:07:42,685
<Default><b>- You have to change out of this! Quickly!
- Sadeena.</b></Default>

138
00:07:42,709 --> 00:07:44,026
<Default><b>- What are you talking about?
- That hurts.</b></Default>

139
00:07:44,050 --> 00:07:45,855
<Default><b>Is everything
okay, Naofumi?</b></Default>

140
00:07:45,879 --> 00:07:46,946
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Yeah.</b></Default>

141
00:07:46,970 --> 00:07:49,610
<Default><b>You need to calm down.
Tell me what's happening.</b></Default>

142
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:51,985
<Default><b>I will as soon
as she changes her clothes!</b></Default>

143
00:07:52,009 --> 00:07:55,230
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Fine.
Raphtalia, go and change.</b></Default>

144
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:57,850
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

145
00:07:58,230 --> 00:08:00,269
<Default><b>Aw, but it looks
good on her.</b></Default>

146
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,456
<Default><b>[DEMI-HUMAN GIRL 12-B]
That's no fun.</b></Default>

147
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:03,836
<Default><b>[DEMI-HUMAN GIRL 12-A]
Why can't she wear it?</b></Default>

148
00:08:03,860 --> 00:08:05,620
<Default><b>What has
gotten into you?</b></Default>

149
00:08:06,069 --> 00:08:07,755
<Default><b>Wearing that outfit
is the same as</b></Default>

150
00:08:07,779 --> 00:08:09,466
<Default><b>painting a target
on her back.</b></Default>

151
00:08:09,490 --> 00:08:12,255
<Default><b>It tells the world she's next
in line for the throne.</b></Default>

152
00:08:12,279 --> 00:08:13,319
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

153
00:08:13,949 --> 00:08:15,790
<Default><b>Wha... Hey!</b></Default>

154
00:08:16,459 --> 00:08:18,370
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

155
00:08:21,290 --> 00:08:22,650
<Default><b>I was too late!</b></Default>

156
00:08:22,709 --> 00:08:25,050
<Default><b>As source of thy power</b></Default>

157
00:08:25,129 --> 00:08:27,009
<Default><b>Decipher the
laws of nature.</b></Default>

158
00:08:29,589 --> 00:08:30,800
<Default><b>Raphtalia!</b></Default>

159
00:08:33,509 --> 00:08:34,576
<Default><b>A kunai?</b></Default>

160
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,889
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

161
00:08:38,139 --> 00:08:39,706
<Default><b>- It's an ambush!
- Damn it!</b></Default>

162
00:08:39,730 --> 00:08:41,535
<Default><b>Eclair and the old lady
aren't around either!</b></Default>

163
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:42,916
<Default><b>[MONKEY 12-A (M)] Die!</b></Default>

164
00:08:42,940 --> 00:08:45,360
<Default><b>Lightning strike those
standing before me</b></Default>

165
00:08:45,570 --> 00:08:47,490
<Default><b>All Drifa Chain
Lightning!</b></Default>

166
00:08:49,990 --> 00:08:51,046
<Default><b>Are you okay?</b></Default>

167
00:08:51,070 --> 00:08:52,870
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
Yes, thank you!</b></Default>

168
00:08:53,490 --> 00:08:55,556
<Default><b>Sir Itsuki we have
to help them fight back!</b></Default>

169
00:08:55,580 --> 00:08:56,806
<Default><b>I'll see what I can do.</b></Default>

170
00:08:56,830 --> 00:08:58,096
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
She's badly wounded.</b></Default>

171
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,265
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
Rishia, please!</b></Default>

172
00:08:59,289 --> 00:09:00,895
<Default><b>[RISHIA]
Leave her to me!</b></Default>

173
00:09:00,919 --> 00:09:02,186
<Default><b>[ELHART]
What's going on over there?</b></Default>

174
00:09:02,210 --> 00:09:03,476
<Default><b>[ATLA]
Was that an explosion?</b></Default>

175
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:05,525
<Default><b>I don't know
I came as fast as I...</b></Default>

176
00:09:05,549 --> 00:09:07,025
<Default><b>[FOX 12-A (M)]
Don't try and deny it.</b></Default>

177
00:09:07,049 --> 00:09:08,769
<Default><b>We saw your declaration!</b></Default>

178
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:10,816
<Default><b>We'll do whatever it takes
to stop you</b></Default>

179
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,520
<Default><b>from taking the throne!</b></Default>

180
00:09:13,470 --> 00:09:14,985
<Default><b>Who are these people?</b></Default>

181
00:09:15,009 --> 00:09:17,329
<Default><b>And what is this 'throne"
they speak of?</b></Default>

182
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:20,440
<Default><b>First thing's first.
We must protect Raphtalia!</b></Default>

183
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:23,199
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Meteor Shield!</b></Default>

184
00:09:24,730 --> 00:09:26,110
<Default><b>What the!</b></Default>

185
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,360
<Default><b>I'll use my
Hundred Swords!</b></Default>

186
00:09:29,649 --> 00:09:31,649
<Default><b>And I'll use Arrow Rain!</b></Default>

187
00:09:40,039 --> 00:09:41,620
<Default><b>Air Strike Shield!</b></Default>

188
00:09:43,379 --> 00:09:47,049
<Default><b>- Now, Raphtalia!
- I'm on it! Brave Blade Mist!</b></Default>

189
00:09:49,259 --> 00:09:50,899
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
He's tough!</b></Default>

190
00:09:54,470 --> 00:09:56,070
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
That worked?</b></Default>

191
00:09:56,259 --> 00:09:57,639
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

192
00:10:04,269 --> 00:10:05,610
<Default><b>Don't tell me.</b></Default>

193
00:10:08,190 --> 00:10:10,350
<Default><b>They're only immune
to Hero attacks?</b></Default>

194
00:10:11,149 --> 00:10:12,669
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Raphtalia!</b></Default>

195
00:10:14,700 --> 00:10:17,539
<Default><b>I don't know if
this will work</b></Default>

196
00:10:17,620 --> 00:10:18,806
<Default><b>Understood!</b></Default>

197
00:10:18,830 --> 00:10:20,330
<Default><b>Oh, Power of two</b></Default>

198
00:10:20,450 --> 00:10:22,710
<Default><b>bewilder the enemy
with an illusion!</b></Default>

199
00:10:22,909 --> 00:10:25,169
<Default><b>Spin the threads of fate
once more.</b></Default>

200
00:10:25,419 --> 00:10:26,476
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA, NAOFUMI]
And thereby turn</b></Default>

201
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:28,220
<Default><b>our defeat into victory!</b></Default>

202
00:10:28,379 --> 00:10:29,645
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA, NAOFUMI]
Dragon Vein</b></Default>

203
00:10:29,669 --> 00:10:32,220
<Default><b>hear our plea
and grant us your power!</b></Default>

204
00:10:32,379 --> 00:10:35,129
<Default><b>As source of thy power</b></Default>

205
00:10:35,340 --> 00:10:37,350
<Default><b>Decipher the
laws of nature</b></Default>

206
00:10:37,429 --> 00:10:40,559
<Default><b>and create an illusion
to deceive my foes!</b></Default>

207
00:10:41,230 --> 00:10:43,035
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA, NAOFUMI]
Form is emptiness!</b></Default>

208
00:10:43,059 --> 00:10:45,350
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

209
00:10:52,110 --> 00:10:53,450
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

210
00:10:55,860 --> 00:10:57,380
<Default><b>What just happened?</b></Default>

211
00:10:57,409 --> 00:10:59,176
<Default><b>We used some
Choral magic.</b></Default>

212
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:02,240
<Default><b>It's not much but it'll keep
them busy for a little while.</b></Default>

213
00:11:02,370 --> 00:11:04,096
<Default><b>[REN] For whatever reason
they seem resistant</b></Default>

214
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,520
<Default><b>to Hero attacks.</b></Default>

215
00:11:05,710 --> 00:11:07,105
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] We'll just have
to use our big moves</b></Default>

216
00:11:07,129 --> 00:11:08,686
<Default><b>to overwhelm
their defenses.</b></Default>

217
00:11:08,710 --> 00:11:10,015
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Exactly.</b></Default>

218
00:11:10,039 --> 00:11:11,645
<Default><b>[REN] All right, then.</b></Default>

219
00:11:11,669 --> 00:11:14,340
<Default><b>Here it goes!
Meteor Slash!</b></Default>

220
00:11:14,509 --> 00:11:17,049
<Default><b>Eagle Piercing Shot!</b></Default>

221
00:11:17,470 --> 00:11:21,309
<Default><b>Eight Trigrams
Blade of Destiny!</b></Default>

222
00:11:22,809 --> 00:11:26,769
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

223
00:11:34,990 --> 00:11:37,700
<Default><b>[ORCA 12-A (M)] Glory be to
the Heavenly Emperor!</b></Default>

224
00:11:39,029 --> 00:11:40,529
<Default><b>Get to cover!</b></Default>

225
00:11:40,909 --> 00:11:42,200
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

226
00:11:43,289 --> 00:11:44,700
<Default><b>What's happened?</b></Default>

227
00:11:46,370 --> 00:11:47,830
<Default><b>Hyah!</b></Default>

228
00:11:54,259 --> 00:11:56,509
<Default><b>I think you owe me
an explanation.</b></Default>

229
00:11:58,679 --> 00:12:02,389
<Default><b>Those assassins</b></Default>

230
00:12:02,509 --> 00:12:04,429
<Default><b>came here from Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

231
00:12:05,389 --> 00:12:06,809
<Default><b>From Q'ten Lo?</b></Default>

232
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:15,279
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

233
00:12:16,570 --> 00:12:17,926
<Default><b>[DEMI-HUMAN GIRL 12-C]
Here!</b></Default>

234
00:12:17,950 --> 00:12:19,270
<Default><b>[KEEL] Got it!</b></Default>

235
00:12:20,110 --> 00:12:21,550
<Default><b>[SADEENA] You see</b></Default>

236
00:12:21,659 --> 00:12:23,059
<Default><b>about Raphtalia.</b></Default>

237
00:12:23,159 --> 00:12:25,176
<Default><b>She was born
into a royal family.</b></Default>

238
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,960
<Default><b>The family of Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

239
00:12:27,289 --> 00:12:29,226
<Default><b>She's a descendant
of the Emperor.</b></Default>

240
00:12:29,250 --> 00:12:30,379
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

241
00:12:34,919 --> 00:12:37,025
<Default><b>And what does that have to do
with the miko outfit</b></Default>

242
00:12:37,049 --> 00:12:38,449
<Default><b>she was wearing?</b></Default>

243
00:12:38,879 --> 00:12:41,519
<Default><b>[SADEENA] The robe you refer
to as a miko outfit</b></Default>

244
00:12:42,850 --> 00:12:44,155
<Default><b>it's a special attire</b></Default>

245
00:12:44,179 --> 00:12:46,699
<Default><b>only the Heavenly Empress
is allowed to wear.</b></Default>

246
00:12:46,929 --> 00:12:48,559
<Default><b>This is...</b></Default>

247
00:12:48,940 --> 00:12:51,059
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
And so, when Raphtalia</b></Default>

248
00:12:51,149 --> 00:12:53,029
<Default><b>who is royalty
born wears it</b></Default>

249
00:12:53,519 --> 00:12:56,320
<Default><b>it's no different than
declaring herself Empress.</b></Default>

250
00:12:58,110 --> 00:13:00,450
<Default><b>Since Q'ten Lo already
has an Emperor</b></Default>

251
00:13:00,529 --> 00:13:02,529
<Default><b>this is akin to
declaring war.</b></Default>

252
00:13:03,490 --> 00:13:04,716
<Default><b>This isn't over.</b></Default>

253
00:13:04,740 --> 00:13:07,385
<Default><b>They're sure to send more
assassins in the future.</b></Default>

254
00:13:07,409 --> 00:13:08,765
<Default><b>That's horrible.</b></Default>

255
00:13:08,789 --> 00:13:12,000
<Default><b>Sadeena, Raphtalia's parent
died in this village.</b></Default>

256
00:13:12,580 --> 00:13:14,580
<Default><b>In the midst of
the First Wave.</b></Default>

257
00:13:15,039 --> 00:13:16,605
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Why would
descendants of an Emperor</b></Default>

258
00:13:16,629 --> 00:13:18,309
<Default><b>be in Lurolona Village?</b></Default>

259
00:13:19,340 --> 00:13:20,566
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
Because of a war over</b></Default>

260
00:13:20,590 --> 00:13:22,550
<Default><b>who would be
the next Emperor.</b></Default>

261
00:13:23,549 --> 00:13:25,946
<Default><b>Her father grew tired
of the endless struggles</b></Default>

262
00:13:25,970 --> 00:13:28,570
<Default><b>in the royal family
over who would be the heir.</b></Default>

263
00:13:29,100 --> 00:13:30,826
<Default><b>So he and his wife
fled the country</b></Default>

264
00:13:30,850 --> 00:13:32,450
<Default><b>to come to Melromarc.</b></Default>

265
00:13:33,730 --> 00:13:35,820
<Default><b>My family has served
as bodyguards</b></Default>

266
00:13:35,899 --> 00:13:38,320
<Default><b>for the royal family
for generations.</b></Default>

267
00:13:39,070 --> 00:13:40,966
<Default><b>But I decided
to abandon my mission</b></Default>

268
00:13:40,990 --> 00:13:43,740
<Default><b>so I could follow them
and stand by their side.</b></Default>

269
00:13:45,529 --> 00:13:49,330
<Default><b>After Raphtalia was born</b></Default>

270
00:13:51,460 --> 00:13:55,960
<Default><b>But then... on that day
when the first Wave hit</b></Default>

271
00:13:56,250 --> 00:13:58,355
<Default><b>I was out at sea fishing
and was attacked</b></Default>

272
00:13:58,379 --> 00:14:00,059
<Default><b>by the Wave's monsters.</b></Default>

273
00:14:00,879 --> 00:14:02,775
<Default><b>I couldn't protect
the three of them.</b></Default>

274
00:14:02,799 --> 00:14:04,679
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

275
00:14:05,889 --> 00:14:08,529
<Default><b>[SADEENA] And by the time
I finally made it back</b></Default>

276
00:14:08,769 --> 00:14:11,369
<Default><b>the slavers had already come
and left with her.</b></Default>

277
00:14:12,980 --> 00:14:14,350
<Default><b>In an instant</b></Default>

278
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:16,336
<Default><b>the family
I had sworn to protect</b></Default>

279
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:18,610
<Default><b>with my life
was no more.</b></Default>

280
00:14:24,529 --> 00:14:25,649
<Default><b>Raphtalia</b></Default>

281
00:14:25,990 --> 00:14:28,670
<Default><b>is being the Heavenly Empress
something you want?</b></Default>

282
00:14:28,990 --> 00:14:30,080
<Default><b>No.</b></Default>

283
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:32,300
<Default><b>The fire has
settled down.</b></Default>

284
00:14:32,580 --> 00:14:34,060
<Default><b>Is the child okay?</b></Default>

285
00:14:35,419 --> 00:14:37,819
<Default><b>I wouldn't say
she's out of the woods yet.</b></Default>

286
00:14:42,340 --> 00:14:43,740
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

287
00:14:44,879 --> 00:14:47,220
<Default><b>I see. It was Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

288
00:14:47,299 --> 00:14:48,696
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] The reason
they picked a fight with us</b></Default>

289
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:50,009
<Default><b>was idiotic.</b></Default>

290
00:14:50,639 --> 00:14:51,850
<Default><b>Not quite.</b></Default>

291
00:14:51,929 --> 00:14:54,285
<Default><b>[ECLAIR] Just because it might
seem stupid to us.</b></Default>

292
00:14:54,309 --> 00:14:56,375
<Default><b>Doesn't mean it's not a matter
of life or death</b></Default>

293
00:14:56,399 --> 00:14:57,919
<Default><b>to another country.</b></Default>

294
00:14:58,519 --> 00:15:00,586
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Sadeena, there were times</b></Default>

295
00:15:00,610 --> 00:15:02,166
<Default><b>when you were acting
like there might be someone</b></Default>

296
00:15:02,190 --> 00:15:03,875
<Default><b>on the outskirts
of the village.</b></Default>

297
00:15:03,899 --> 00:15:05,699
<Default><b>Were you
looking for them?</b></Default>

298
00:15:06,070 --> 00:15:07,635
<Default><b>- Yes.
- Then how long</b></Default>

299
00:15:07,659 --> 00:15:09,739
<Default><b>have they been
watching Raphtalia?</b></Default>

300
00:15:11,330 --> 00:15:13,976
<Default><b>They've been watching her
since before she was born.</b></Default>

301
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,620
<Default><b>- I'm sorry.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

302
00:15:16,210 --> 00:15:17,539
<Default><b>Seriously?</b></Default>

303
00:15:17,629 --> 00:15:20,229
<Default><b>So when the First Wave hit
and the slavers came</b></Default>

304
00:15:20,340 --> 00:15:22,380
<Default><b>when she was nearly
auctioned off</b></Default>

305
00:15:22,460 --> 00:15:25,090
<Default><b>when she became my slave
and nearly died.</b></Default>

306
00:15:25,419 --> 00:15:27,155
<Default><b>You mean to tell me
this entire time</b></Default>

307
00:15:27,179 --> 00:15:28,405
<Default><b>they've been
watching her</b></Default>

308
00:15:28,429 --> 00:15:30,509
<Default><b>and did nothing about
any of that?</b></Default>

309
00:15:30,639 --> 00:15:32,115
<Default><b>Can't say I'm surprised.</b></Default>

310
00:15:32,139 --> 00:15:34,155
<Default><b>I hate to say it
but from their perspective</b></Default>

311
00:15:34,179 --> 00:15:36,206
<Default><b>they'd be better off
if she died.</b></Default>

312
00:15:36,230 --> 00:15:38,070
<Default><b>She threatens
their throne.</b></Default>

313
00:15:38,190 --> 00:15:39,836
<Default><b>Yeah, you're
probably right.</b></Default>

314
00:15:39,860 --> 00:15:41,836
<Default><b>But if they'd been
watching that closely</b></Default>

315
00:15:41,860 --> 00:15:44,375
<Default><b>they'd know she wasn't aware
of her royal blood</b></Default>

316
00:15:44,399 --> 00:15:45,966
<Default><b>meaning that
she had no intention</b></Default>

317
00:15:45,990 --> 00:15:47,790
<Default><b>of ever taking
the throne.</b></Default>

318
00:15:49,279 --> 00:15:50,806
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] They're just using
that miko outfit</b></Default>

319
00:15:50,830 --> 00:15:52,716
<Default><b>as an excuse
to finally kill her.</b></Default>

320
00:15:52,740 --> 00:15:55,370
<Default><b>To eliminate any threat
to the Emperor's rule.</b></Default>

321
00:15:55,659 --> 00:15:57,145
<Default><b>They don't give a damn
whether she wants</b></Default>

322
00:15:57,169 --> 00:15:58,436
<Default><b>the throne or not.</b></Default>

323
00:15:58,460 --> 00:15:59,980
<Default><b>They want her dead.</b></Default>

324
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:04,049
<Default><b>They sent assassins
before even sending messengers.</b></Default>

325
00:16:04,259 --> 00:16:06,970
<Default><b>They see no need
for international formalities</b></Default>

326
00:16:07,129 --> 00:16:09,639
<Default><b>since we're a tiny territory
of Melromarc.</b></Default>

327
00:16:10,009 --> 00:16:11,115
<Default><b>[ECLAIR]
Good point.</b></Default>

328
00:16:11,139 --> 00:16:12,865
<Default><b>They probably assumed
attacking us</b></Default>

329
00:16:12,889 --> 00:16:14,615
<Default><b>wouldn't result
in a war for them.</b></Default>

330
00:16:14,639 --> 00:16:16,285
<Default><b>And I'm gonna make certain
they know</b></Default>

331
00:16:16,309 --> 00:16:17,615
<Default><b>they were
wrong about that.</b></Default>

332
00:16:17,639 --> 00:16:19,839
<Default><b>They're sure as hell
getting a fight!</b></Default>

333
00:16:19,980 --> 00:16:21,360
<Default><b>Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

334
00:16:21,610 --> 00:16:23,850
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
They tried to kill Raphtalia</b></Default>

335
00:16:24,149 --> 00:16:26,529
<Default><b>they gravely wounded
one of my citizens</b></Default>

336
00:16:26,700 --> 00:16:28,820
<Default><b>they waged
war on my lands!</b></Default>

337
00:16:29,279 --> 00:16:32,159
<Default><b>[grunts]
It's a declaration of war</b></Default>

338
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:34,135
<Default><b>against one
of the Cardinal Heroes.</b></Default>

339
00:16:34,159 --> 00:16:36,789
<Default><b>With that in mind</b></Default>

340
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:38,726
<Default><b>We can't get ready
for the Phoenix</b></Default>

341
00:16:38,750 --> 00:16:40,726
<Default><b>if we're constantly
watching our backs.</b></Default>

342
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:43,270
<Default><b>There's only one thing
that all of us can do.</b></Default>

343
00:16:43,500 --> 00:16:45,799
<Default><b>[gasps]
Only one thing. You mean!</b></Default>

344
00:16:47,509 --> 00:16:50,149
<Default><b>We're gonna go and have
a little chat with them.</b></Default>

345
00:16:50,470 --> 00:16:54,679
<Default><b>And if that doesn't work</b></Default>

346
00:16:55,769 --> 00:16:57,309
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

347
00:17:06,690 --> 00:17:08,240
<Default><b>[both grunting]</b></Default>

348
00:17:11,779 --> 00:17:14,829
<Default><b>Atla, we don't have
to do this here, you know.</b></Default>

349
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:16,886
<Default><b>Regardless of
where we are</b></Default>

350
00:17:16,910 --> 00:17:19,500
<Default><b>we have to continue
our training. [Gasps]</b></Default>

351
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:23,480
<Default><b>[ATLA] Hello there.</b></Default>

352
00:17:27,630 --> 00:17:29,235
<Default><b>[MIRELIA]
Leave all of the preparations</b></Default>

353
00:17:29,259 --> 00:17:31,499
<Default><b>for the battle
with the Phoenix to us.</b></Default>

354
00:17:31,720 --> 00:17:34,930
<Default><b>I wish your party
a safe journey to Q-ten Lo.</b></Default>

355
00:17:35,299 --> 00:17:36,325
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Thank you.</b></Default>

356
00:17:36,349 --> 00:17:39,269
<Default><b>I will also send knights
to Lurolona Village</b></Default>

357
00:17:39,390 --> 00:17:41,390
<Default><b>guarding it in
your absence.</b></Default>

358
00:17:41,519 --> 00:17:42,666
<Default><b>I don't get it.</b></Default>

359
00:17:42,690 --> 00:17:44,970
<Default><b>Why are you being
so helpful right now?</b></Default>

360
00:17:45,309 --> 00:17:46,956
<Default><b>I don't know
how you did it</b></Default>

361
00:17:46,980 --> 00:17:49,295
<Default><b>but you managed to bring
the four Heroes together</b></Default>

362
00:17:49,319 --> 00:17:50,835
<Default><b>in time for the Phoenix.</b></Default>

363
00:17:50,859 --> 00:17:53,939
<Default><b>[MIRELIA] It would be an insult
to not reward you for that.</b></Default>

364
00:17:54,160 --> 00:17:57,660
<Default><b>In that case, I'd like to know
the fastest route to Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

365
00:17:58,039 --> 00:18:00,476
<Default><b>We don't have a lot of time
to spare at the moment.</b></Default>

366
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:02,710
<Default><b>Sadly, it's as
the Knight Eclair said</b></Default>

367
00:18:02,869 --> 00:18:04,869
<Default><b>Q'ten Lo has
isolated them self</b></Default>

368
00:18:04,920 --> 00:18:07,320
<Default><b>and we don't have
any relations with them.</b></Default>

369
00:18:08,009 --> 00:18:09,815
<Default><b>However, there
is something.</b></Default>

370
00:18:09,839 --> 00:18:12,680
<Default><b>A ferry that goes to Q'ten Lo
from Siltvelt.</b></Default>

371
00:18:13,130 --> 00:18:15,235
<Default><b>I'll see if I can arrange
for you all to be</b></Default>

372
00:18:15,259 --> 00:18:16,656
<Default><b>on the next one out.</b></Default>

373
00:18:16,680 --> 00:18:17,960
<Default><b>Sounds great.</b></Default>

374
00:18:18,099 --> 00:18:19,769
<Default><b>Back to Siltvelt, huh?</b></Default>

375
00:18:19,930 --> 00:18:22,650
<Default><b>That's the place where we
picked up Fohl and Atla.</b></Default>

376
00:18:23,269 --> 00:18:25,456
<Default><b>How are those two?
Are they doing well?</b></Default>

377
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:27,609
<Default><b>Sure are.
They're here right now.</b></Default>

378
00:18:27,730 --> 00:18:29,570
<Default><b>They insist on
following me</b></Default>

379
00:18:29,609 --> 00:18:31,795
<Default><b>whether I really want them to
or not.</b></Default>

380
00:18:31,819 --> 00:18:33,459
<Default><b>I think that's lovely.</b></Default>

381
00:18:33,819 --> 00:18:36,716
<Default><b>[MIRELIA] I suppose they'll be
going to Siltvelt too then.</b></Default>

382
00:18:36,740 --> 00:18:38,260
<Default><b>[FOHL]
Hey, old man!</b></Default>

383
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:40,976
<Default><b>What're you
doing out here?</b></Default>

384
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:43,845
<Default><b>I suggest that you watch
your tone, boy! This here is...</b></Default>

385
00:18:43,869 --> 00:18:45,829
<Default><b>Silence. I'll
hear no more.</b></Default>

386
00:18:45,920 --> 00:18:47,089
<Default><b>Yes, sir.</b></Default>

387
00:18:49,759 --> 00:18:51,759
<Default><b>Are you
feeling all right?</b></Default>

388
00:18:52,380 --> 00:18:54,025
<Default><b>Have you had
enough to eat?</b></Default>

389
00:18:54,049 --> 00:18:55,890
<Default><b>Yes. Thank
you for asking.</b></Default>

390
00:18:56,549 --> 00:18:57,946
<Default><b>[FOHL]
She can eat all right.</b></Default>

391
00:18:57,970 --> 00:19:00,235
<Default><b>Atla eats enough food
for the both of us!</b></Default>

392
00:19:00,259 --> 00:19:02,349
<Default><b>Yes. I'm full of energy.</b></Default>

393
00:19:02,430 --> 00:19:03,730
<Default><b>Ah, I see!</b></Default>

394
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:06,916
<Default><b>The Shield Demon hasn't done
you any harm, has he?</b></Default>

395
00:19:06,940 --> 00:19:08,140
<Default><b>[BOTH] Huh?</b></Default>

396
00:19:08,980 --> 00:19:10,580
<Default><b>Did you say, "Demon?"</b></Default>

397
00:19:10,819 --> 00:19:13,740
<Default><b>Please don't use such
a terribly cruel word as that.</b></Default>

398
00:19:14,950 --> 00:19:16,295
<Default><b>I mean after all</b></Default>

399
00:19:16,319 --> 00:19:19,450
<Default><b>it's thanks to Master Naofumi
that I'm even alive right now.</b></Default>

400
00:19:19,910 --> 00:19:21,345
<Default><b>[FOHL]
Yeah, that's right.</b></Default>

401
00:19:21,369 --> 00:19:23,489
<Default><b>Atla was getting sicker
by the day.</b></Default>

402
00:19:23,660 --> 00:19:26,220
<Default><b>She never would've
recovered without his help.</b></Default>

403
00:19:26,420 --> 00:19:29,460
<Default><b>She was so sick</b></Default>

404
00:19:31,630 --> 00:19:33,190
<Default><b>But look at her now!</b></Default>

405
00:19:36,759 --> 00:19:38,025
<Default><b>[ATLA]
Oh, there he is!</b></Default>

406
00:19:38,049 --> 00:19:39,349
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

407
00:19:39,599 --> 00:19:41,099
<Default><b>[grunts] Farewell.</b></Default>

408
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:45,230
<Default><b>[ATLA] Oh! Um, will we ever
get to see you again?</b></Default>

409
00:19:46,849 --> 00:19:49,480
<Default><b>Yes. I'm certain of it.</b></Default>

410
00:19:56,779 --> 00:19:59,119
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] And so...
I left Queen Mirelia</b></Default>

411
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:01,000
<Default><b>in charge of
preparations.</b></Default>

412
00:20:01,829 --> 00:20:03,619
<Default><b>And headed for Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

413
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:07,880
<Default><b>First, we'll head to Siltvelt
where the ferry departs.</b></Default>

414
00:20:08,329 --> 00:20:10,356
<Default><b>I'll fly there
with Wyndia and Gaelion.</b></Default>

415
00:20:10,380 --> 00:20:12,396
<Default><b>Once we're in a safe
enough location.</b></Default>

416
00:20:12,420 --> 00:20:15,300
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I'll use a portal
to summon the rest of you.</b></Default>

417
00:20:15,420 --> 00:20:17,140
<Default><b>Be careful flying there!</b></Default>

418
00:20:17,259 --> 00:20:19,140
<Default><b>Take care of
him, all right?</b></Default>

419
00:20:19,299 --> 00:20:20,825
<Default><b>We're all
counting on you!</b></Default>

420
00:20:20,849 --> 00:20:22,259
<Default><b>[soft roaring]</b></Default>

421
00:20:22,509 --> 00:20:23,866
<Default><b>Just leave it to me!</b></Default>

422
00:20:23,890 --> 00:20:25,410
<Default><b>You all hang tight.</b></Default>

423
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:33,230
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

424
00:20:34,940 --> 00:20:36,335
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
We have less than two months</b></Default>

425
00:20:36,359 --> 00:20:38,200
<Default><b>before the
Phoenix revives.</b></Default>

426
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:41,466
<Default><b>What I'm doing now
might be irresponsible</b></Default>

427
00:20:41,490 --> 00:20:43,370
<Default><b>given the time
we have left.</b></Default>

428
00:20:44,039 --> 00:20:47,500
<Default><b>However... this is a battle
I have to fight.</b></Default>

429
00:20:48,170 --> 00:20:51,539
<Default><b>After all, this will decide
Raphtalia's fate!</b></Default>

430
00:20:52,210 --> 00:20:54,210
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

431
00:20:55,420 --> 00:20:57,470
<Default><b>- [giggling]
- Raphy.</b></Default>

432
00:20:58,420 --> 00:20:59,630
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

433
00:20:59,720 --> 00:21:02,339
<Default><b>Slow down, Filo!
You're too fast!</b></Default>

434
00:21:06,220 --> 00:21:07,890
<Default><b>[FILO] Here we go!</b></Default>

435
00:21:08,230 --> 00:21:10,030
<Default><b>Just wait and
see, Master!</b></Default>

436
00:21:10,059 --> 00:21:12,745
<Default><b>I'm gonna come back
ten times stronger than before!</b></Default>

437
00:21:12,769 --> 00:21:13,940
<Default><b>Ra-Raphy.</b></Default>

438
00:21:14,019 --> 00:21:17,029
<Default><b>- Wait, before we go.
- [FILO] And we're off!</b></Default>

439
00:21:17,990 --> 00:21:20,136
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Even though
I'm the Shield Hero</b></Default>

440
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:23,160
<Default><b>I shouldn't interfere with
the fates of my party members.</b></Default>

441
00:21:23,569 --> 00:21:25,609
<Default><b>But they're my precious
comrades.</b></Default>

442
00:21:26,039 --> 00:21:27,845
<Default><b>And for the sake
of those comrades</b></Default>

443
00:21:27,869 --> 00:21:30,250
<Default><b>I'll fight the Waves</b></Default>

444
00:21:30,329 --> 00:21:32,489
<Default><b>and anything else
that comes my way!</b></Default>

445
00:21:32,829 --> 00:21:34,630
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

446
00:21:37,589 --> 00:21:40,630
<Default><b>Worry not. For the sake
of my precious Filo</b></Default>

447
00:21:40,720 --> 00:21:42,720
<Default><b>I will fight
by your side</b></Default>

448
00:21:45,509 --> 00:21:48,189
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I'll fight
an entire country if I must!</b></Default>

449
00:21:48,470 --> 00:21:50,769
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

450
00:21:55,019 --> 00:21:56,499
<Default><b>[thunder rumbling]</b></Default>

451
00:21:56,900 --> 00:21:59,240
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Because</b></Default>

452
00:21:59,319 --> 00:22:01,239
<Default><b>the Shield Hero,
must follow!</b></Default>

453
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:05,079
<Default><b>[thunder rumbling]</b></Default>

